<li><a href='http://repo.oddthesis.org/maven2/org/jboss/rails/jboss-rails/1.0.0.Beta4/jboss-rails-1.0.0.Beta4-deployer.jar' title='JBoss-Rails Deployer'>The standalone JBoss-Rails deployer jar</a> (~30mb, drag'n'drop, you're done)</li>
